37#ifndef ASCII_H
38#define ASCII_H
39
40/*
41 * just name the common ASCII control codes
42 */
43#define NUL 0
44#define SOH 1
45#define STX 2
46#define ETX 3
47#define EOT 4
48#define ENQ 5
49#define ACK 6
50#define BEL 7
51#define BS 8
52#define HT 9
53#define NL 10
54#define VT 11
55#define NP 12
56#define CR 13
57#define SO 14
58#define SI 15
59#define DLE 16
60#define DC1 17
61#define DC2 18
62#define DC3 19
63#define DC4 20
64#define NAK 21
65#define SYN 22
66#define ETB 23
67#define CAN 24
68#define EM 25
69#define SUB 26
70#define ESC 27
71#define FS 28
72#define GS 29
73#define RS 30
74#define US 31
75#define SP 32
76#define DEL 127
77
78#endif
